- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possible category as the paper deals with the complexity of maintaining queries under changes. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper studies the maintainability of context-free languages under changes. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also possible as the paper deals with the maintenance of queries under changes, which is a common topic in database management systems.
